{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji12.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给吴亮平·的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给吴亮平的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年6月15日）亮平同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接了美国一位同情者的信，我想请你起草一封回信。信内除感谢她外，并说及八路抗战情形，请她转告美国兄弟姊妹们多给我们援助，我们和他们是站在一起的。如何，盼示！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月十五日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]吴亮平（1908一1986)，浙江奉化人。当时在延安编辑《解放》周刊。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1938,"month":6,"day":15}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":358,"page_end":358},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}